          name: 'Cohen MH, Gootenberg J, Keegan P, Pazdur R. FDA Drug Approval Summary: Bevacizumab (Avastin) Plus Carboplatin and Paclitaxel as First-Line Treatment of Advanced/Metastatic Recurrent Nonsquamous Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer. The Oncologist. 2007;12(6):713-718.',
          url: 'https://academic.oup.com/oncolo/article/12/6/713/6410402',
